72-820.Mayhew Cabin historical site; Game and Parks Commission; powers.

The Game and Parks Commission may purchase or receive by donation, and subsequently rehabilitate and manage, the Mayhew Cabin historical site located in Nebraska City, Nebraska.

SourceLaws 2023, LB531, ยง 54;Laws 2025, LB264, ยง 154.Operative Date: May 22, 2025
